{"id":258290,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-上海维权者联名要求释放失踪多日的张俊/","date":"2012-10-21T03:15:48Z","modified":"2012-10-21T03:15:48Z","title":"维权网 | 上海维权者联名要求释放失踪多日的张俊国夫妇（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日上午</span><span>，深圳维权人士杨林得到消息：今天约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>分左右，张宏波、张静波、马波、刘纯宝、胖胖等五维权人士，在江苏省南通市港闸区张贴印有失踪访民张俊国、徐丽艳夫妇照片的寻人启事。遭到江苏省南通市港闸区公安机构派出一台警车与六至七台黑车、四十多人将张宏波、张静波、马波、刘纯宝、胖胖等五维权人士所乘坐的汽车包围，并且，警察动手打五名维权人士。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>江苏省南通市维权人士张俊国、徐丽艳夫妇俩合法经营的《江苏省南通市红枫丽莱木业公司一号桥地板厂》的厂房于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日</span><span>遭到南通市政府和深圳华强北集团官商勾结强拆，造成张俊国、徐丽艳夫妻数千万财产损失。非法暴力强拆之后，张俊国、徐丽艳夫妇向南通市公安局港闸分局、检察院、法院要求立案，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">400</span><span>多天无结果。因此，夫妇俩从地方上访到中央，无人给一个说法。张俊国、徐丽艳夫妇一夜之间从千万富翁变为乞丐。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>时许，张俊国、徐丽艳夫妇正在和朋友一起吃晚饭时，遭到南通市公安局港闸分局非法抓捕，至今下落不明。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>，北京市新桥律师事务所李静林律师同张俊国、徐丽艳夫妇的两个儿子（张宏波、张静波）和媳妇一起到南通市公安局港闸分局申请信息公开，要求警方公开抓张俊国、徐丽艳夫妇的理由和手续。港闸区分局督察部门一位郭姓的负责人不肯告知办理信息公开的是哪一个部门。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海部分上访维权人士（附：签名单）为了伸张正义、反对腐败、反对掠夺、要求南通市公安局港闸区分局立即释放张俊国、徐丽艳夫妇。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>杨林电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13538281848</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-VzxoRFrXwHo/UINbcepqPfI/AAAAAAAARm8/vHB7tm_Op50/s1600/%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%B3%E9%87%8A%E6%94%BE%E7%BB%B4%E6%9D%83%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E5%BE%90%E4%B8%BD%E8%89%B3%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%BB.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-VzxoRFrXwHo/UINbcepqPfI/AAAAAAAARm8/vHB7tm_Op50/s320/%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%B3%E9%87%8A%E6%94%BE%E7%BB%B4%E6%9D%83%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E5%BE%90%E4%B8%BD%E8%89%B3%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%BB.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>上海维权者要求立即释放徐丽艳夫妻</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-IjLOg729ZwE/UINbgEES3oI/AAAAAAAARnE/DgX2ocJOsUA/s1600/PTDC0045.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"253\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-IjLOg729ZwE/UINbgEES3oI/AAAAAAAARnE/DgX2ocJOsUA/s320/PTDC0045.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4fjWMKJ65DQ/UINbjtJOL4I/AAAAAAAARnM/tmnyLKNC_2k/s1600/2010%E5%B9%B410%E6%9C%883%E6%97%A5%E6%89%93%E7%A0%B8%E6%8A%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E5%BC%BA%E6%8B%86.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4fjWMKJ65DQ/UINbjtJOL4I/AAAAAAAARnM/tmnyLKNC_2k/s320/2010%E5%B9%B410%E6%9C%883%E6%97%A5%E6%89%93%E7%A0%B8%E6%8A%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E5%BC%BA%E6%8B%86.JPG\" width=\"235\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-aQwiFxnQ2Sg/UINbnf09FiI/AAAAAAAARnU/2TbhS7w3Gyc/s1600/%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D%E7%AC%AC1%E9%A1%B5.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-aQwiFxnQ2Sg/UINbnf09FiI/AAAAAAAARnU/2TbhS7w3Gyc/s320/%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D%E7%AC%AC1%E9%A1%B5.JPG\" width=\"233\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>要求释放徐丽艳夫妇的签名第1页</td>\n</tr>\n<